# Consolidated — merged from main + GPT-5.6 Sol High discovery branch
# See MERGE-CONSOLIDATION.md for sources

## Two-Pillar Foundation

### Workhorse (60-70% execution)
Haiku 4.5, Gemini Flash, Grok, Composer — Cmd+K edits, boilerplate, implementation.
Never GPT-5.6 for inline edits.

### Decision / Advise / Architect (<10K tokens per model)
GPT-5.6 Sol for decision-making, advice, architect planning — budgeted via `llm_gpt_policy`.
Opus 4.8 / Fable 5 for compliance-heavy architect. Sonnet 5 for verify.

## Token Stack (from main)
- `engine/llm_token_saver.py` — tiktoken, zstd cache, EW bypass
- `engine/llm_gpt_policy.py` — 10K cap per model, GPT allowed
- `engine/token_saver_registry.py` — llm-token-optimizer, tokenpruner, cachetic
- `engine/architect_budget.py` — SaaS architect/decision prompts
- `tools/github_context.py` — cached GitHub summaries

## Install token savers
```bash
.venv/bin/python scripts/install_token_savers.py
.venv/bin/python scripts/architect_budget_check.py --task architect
```

